text.section:
In form and content acceptable to the Department, an applicant for financial assistance from the Fund shall submit to the Department an application that contains:
the information that the Department or Authority considers necessary to evaluate the request for financial assistance; and
for a qualified distressed county project:
a marketing plan designed to market the project to prospective businesses;
a statement of planned marketing expenditures as a percent of the total financial assistance amount requested; and
a plan for the project that is consistent with the county's local strategic economic development plan as to the location and type of project.
